                "name": "Tips From The Guide",
                "type": "section",
                "sections": [],
                "text": "You might allow PCs who <a aonid=\"514\" game-obj=\"Actions\">Follow the Expert</a> when led by a guide to continue to add their level to the skill check for some time afterward: 1 hour if the guide is an expert, 1 day for master, or 1 week for legendary. (The guide here has expert <a aonid=\"3\" game-obj=\"Skills\">Athletics</a>, <a aonid=\"8\" game-obj=\"Skills\">Scouting Lore</a>, and <a aonid=\"16\" game-obj=\"Skills\">Survival</a>.) A character can have this benefit for only one skill at a time.",
